      <title>Ninja Van 推迟 IPO 计划，直至盈利能力改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/ninja-van-holding-off-on-ipo-plans-until-profitability-improves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[物流提供商 Ninja Van 已将上市计划搁置一旁，这是科技初创公司在整个行业估值下跌中苦苦挣扎的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/ninja-van-holding-off-on-ipo-plans-until-profitability-improves</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 09:44:15 GMT</pubDate>
