    <item>
      <title>中国超便宜的电动汽车为普通美国买家带来希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/chinese-ev-affordability-frightens-ford-gm-us-automakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比亚迪售价低于 10,000 美元的 Seagull 电动汽车为全球汽车制造商树立了新标杆，迫使底特律转向更便宜的乘车方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/chinese-ev-affordability-frightens-ford-gm-us-automakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 09:30:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟考虑与美国一起审查中国传统芯片的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/eu-weighs-joining-us-in-reviewing-risks-of-chinese-legacy-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟正在考虑对其企业使用来自中国的成熟或低端芯片的广泛程度进行正式审查，与美国一起指出对国家安全和全球供应链的潜在风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/eu-weighs-joining-us-in-reviewing-risks-of-chinese-legacy-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 09:19:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果正在洽谈让 Google Gemini 为 iPhone 人工智能功能提供支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/apple-in-talks-to-license-google-gemini-for-iphone-ios-18-generative-ai-tools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司正在就将谷歌的 Gemini 人工智能引擎内置到 iPhone 中进行谈判，这为一项震撼人工智能行业的重磅协议奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/apple-in-talks-to-license-google-gemini-for-iphone-ios-18-generative-ai-tools</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 05:23:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>倒下的英国科技明星林奇为避免因欺诈而入狱而奋斗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/fallen-uk-tech-star-lynch-in-fight-to-avoid-us-prison-for-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曾经著名的英国科技企业家迈克·林奇 (Mike Lynch) 因 2011 年与惠普公司 (Hewlett Packard Co.) 的不幸交易而在伦敦民事审判中败诉，之后已经面临着可能的财务破产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/fallen-uk-tech-star-lynch-in-fight-to-avoid-us-prison-for-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大韩航空即将达成约 20 架空客 A350 宽体喷气机的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/korean-air-nears-significant-deal-for-airbus-a350-widebody-jets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，大韩航空即将签署一份空客 SE 宽体喷气式飞机的大订单，该公司希望在与韩亚航空合并后简化其机队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/korean-air-nears-significant-deal-for-airbus-a350-widebody-jets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 02:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于未售出库存堆积，索尼暂停 PSVR2 生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/sony-hits-pause-on-psvr2-production-as-unsold-inventory-piles-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，索尼集团公司已暂停其 PSVR2 耳机的生产，直到清除积压的未售出设备，这加剧了人们对虚拟现实设备吸引力的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/sony-hits-pause-on-psvr2-production-as-unsold-inventory-piles-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 01:56:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电看多者无视巴菲特押注即将到来的人工智能时代的警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/tsmc-bulls-ignore-buffett-s-warning-for-bet-on-coming-ai-age</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对人工智能的狂热正在超越对台积电的地缘政治担忧，其创纪录的股价上涨势头强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/tsmc-bulls-ignore-buffett-s-warning-for-bet-on-coming-ai-age</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 01:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小米撼动中国电动汽车行业，让竞争对手小鹏汽车保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/xiaomi-shakes-up-chinese-ev-sector-keeping-rival-xpeng-on-its-toes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小米公司进军电动汽车领域，以及它将如何撼动中国汽车行业，将在本周与老牌竞争对手小鹏汽车一起公布财报时受到密切关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/xiaomi-shakes-up-chinese-ev-sector-keeping-rival-xpeng-on-its-toes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
